<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dolphin Show</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/hurghada/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Dolphin Show</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        Dolphin Show este una dintre cele mai frumose excursii pentru adulti si copii unde va puteti bucura de un spectcol al delfinilor  a leului de mare si foca.
        Plecarea  va fi in jurul orei 09: 30 in functie de hotelul unde sunteti cazati iar sosirea in jurul orei 13 : 00 in functie de hotelul unde sunteti cazati si de trafic.
        <br>Pret:<br>
        Adult: 20 €<br>
        Copil: 10 €<br><br>
        Cand:<br>
        in fiecare zi  exceptand ziua de sambata   <br><br>
        * Aveti posibilitatea sa inotati alaturi de animalele marine .<br>
        * Inot cu delfini in piscine - 5 minute 50 €<br>
        * Pentru inot cu delfini in piscina progrmarea se face cu 2 zile inainte<br>
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        Dolphin Show is one of the most beautiful excursions for adults and children where you can enjoy a dolphin show of the sea lion and the seal.
        Departure will be around 09:30 depending on the hotel where you are staying and arrival around 13:00 depending on the hotel where you are staying and traffic.        <br><br>
        Price:<br>
        Adult: 20 €<br>
        Children: 10 €
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
        every day except Saturday<br><br>
        * You can swim with marine animals<br>
        * Swimming with dolphins in the pools - 5 minutes 50 € <br>
        * For swimming with dolphins in the pool the appointment is made 2 days before <br>
    </p>
</body>
<script>
    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>